scenario
player uses syphon tree on a tree and then moves to pick up the loot

given
player is facing a tree
tree has 100% chance to drop loot

when
player presses interact button

then
broadcast to all users playerNumber has pressed interact

then
all player wil have that playerNumber use siphon tree on the tree infront
the tree will drop loot

then
the player will press the move key

then
broadcast to all player that playerNumber has moved into that tile with the loot
all player have loot removed and player stats updated
